/span></p>\n<p>CC by.</p>','urban-collision','','','','The shadow','','','',''),(42,1,2,'','','urban-collision','','','','copy of Urban collision','','','',''),(43,1,1,'<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Another Siam shot. This time I was more focused on the life in the streets. I really liked the person crossing the street with patience - and a pink umbrella.</p><p></p>','<p>Une oeuvre de <span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">Marco Nürnberger.</span></p>\n<p>CC by.</p>','urban-collision','','','','Pink Umbrella','','','',''),(43,1,2,'','','urban-collision','','','','copy of Urban collision','','','',''),(44,1,1,'<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Still thinking a lot about Thailand - even 1,5 years after visiting this exciting country.</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">This is a re-editing of one of my \"downtown Siam\" pictures. I really enjoy the possibilities of Nik filters... ;-)</span></p><p></p>','<p>Une oeuvre de <span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">Marco Nürnberger.</span></p>\n<p>CC by.</p>','urban-collision','','','','Supercenter','','','',''),(44,1,2,'','','urban-collision','','','','copy of Urban collision','','','',''),(45,1,1,'<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Our fun stop wehn driving home from Brugge to Germany. Atomium is really a great fun for young and old \"kids\". Of course I had to do some long exposures before leaving Bruxelles.</p><p></p>\n<p></p>','<p>Une oeuvre de <span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">Marco Nürnberger.</span></p>\n<p>CC by.</p>','urban-collision','','','','Atomium','','','',''),(45,1,2,'','','urban-collision','','','','copy of Urban collision','','','',''),(46,1,1,'<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Our last evening in our small but lovely cottage at Paloma beach.</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Two facts about this image:</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">1. yes, the sunset was really impressive</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">2. yes, I did far too much editing on this image</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">... but somehow, I like it :-)</span></p><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>','<p>Une oeuvre de <span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">Marco Nürnberger.</span></p>\n<p>CC by.</p>','urban-collision','','','','Over the Top','','','',''),(46,1,2,'','','urban-collision','','','','copy of Urban collision','','','',''),(47,1,1,'<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Real Alcázar is worth it!</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">A island in the middle of Sevilla, full of nature and culture.</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">From a photographic perspective the \"Baños de Doña María\" provide a lot of fun - you don\'t even need a tripod - the little wall in front of the bath does its job just perfectly.</span></p><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>','<p>Une oeuvre de <span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">Marco Nürnberger.</span></p>\n<p>CC by.</p>','urban-collision','','','','Los Baños','','','',''),(47,1,2,'','','urban-collision','','','','copy of Urban collision','','','',''),(48,1,1,'<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">One of my favorites of the Netherlands holiday - shot near Oostkapelle, Zeeland. The geo data is random - there are too many pales at this beach. Nikon - why don\'t you include GPS in your cameras?</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">The afternoon was great for some long exposures with clouds passing by.</span></p>','<p>Une oeuvre de <span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">Marco Nürnberger.</span></p>\n<p>CC by.</p>','urban-collision','','','','Rising Tides','','','',''),(48,1,2,'','','urban-collision','','','','copy of Urban collision','','','',''),(49,1,1,'<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Another great cityscape in Rotterdam - the Erasmus Bridge.</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" id=\"yui_3_16_0_1_1556734894413_75995\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">It rained a lot this evening - big thanks to Johanna for her patience.</span></p><p></p>','<p>Une oeuvre de <span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">Marco Nürnberger.</span></p>\n<p>CC by.</p>','urban-collision','','','','Iron Strings','','','',''),(49,1,2,'','','urban-collision','','','','copy of Urban collision','','','',''),(50,1,1,'<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">My only sunrise trip during our Netherlands/Belgium holliday.</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">I really had luck with the clouds passing by.</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">But the editing of this picture wasn\'t easy.</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">So together with two friends of mine, I did a \"we edit your raw\"-Session.</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Felix had the idea to give the picture a lot of warmth - more like sunset instead of sunrise.</span></p><p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">I always had a black and white conversion in my mind, but this editing really fascinated me - so the final image is \"sponsored by Felix\" :-)</span></p>\n<p></p>','<p>Une oeuvre de <span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">Marco Nü